        text: "' ========================================================="
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Class:    cRegistry"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Author:   Steve McMahon"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Date  :   21 Feb 1997"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' A nice class wrapper around the registry functions"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Allows searching,deletion,modification and addition"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' of Keys or Values."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Updated 29 April 1998 for VB5."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Fixed GPF in EnumerateValues"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Added support for all registry types, not just strings"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Put all declares in local class"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Added VB5 Enums"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Added CreateKey and DeleteKey methods"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Updated 2 January 1999"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * The CreateExeAssociation method failed to set up the"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     association correctly if the optional document icon"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     was not provided."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Added new parameters to CreateExeAssociation to set up"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     other standard handlers: Print, Add, New"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Provided the CreateAdditionalEXEAssociations method"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     to allow non-standard menu items to be added (for example,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     right click on a .VBP file.  VB installs Run and Make"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     menu items)."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Updated 8 February 2000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   * Ensure CreateExeAssociation and related items sets up the"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     registry keys in the"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'           HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Classes"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     branch as well as the HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT branch."
      - kind: Newline
